In the exercise, Lithuania represented by over 300 troops and over 50 tactical vehicles from the Lithuanian Grand Duchess Birute Uhlan Battalion, Colonel Juozas Vitkus Engineer Battalion of the Lithuanian Land Force and the 2nd Territorial Unit of Darius and Girenas Military District of the National Defence Volunteer Force.&#160;

