&#8220;Following extensive investigation, security forces successfully captured the network responsible for the SYL Hotel terrorist attack, arresting 16 suspects, including the mastermind Abdinasir Dahir Nur. Justice will be served in court for all involved,&#8221; Nisa said in a statement on X (formerly Twitter).&#160;

